Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:45.54,CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\b1\fn@华文中宋\be0\frz-90\bord0\shad0\fs24\fsp-4\c&H090909&\pos(938,238)}哼-----說到底
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:45.54,CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\b1\fn@华文中宋\be0\frz-90\bord0\shad0\fs24\fsp-4\c&H090909&\pos(975,332)}就是選好食材、絕不後悔而已
