Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:19.23,CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\b0\fn黑体\be0\bord0\shad0\fs28\fsp-2\c&H090909&\frz4.9\pos(936,356)}我一整天都無所事事…
