Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:19.23,CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\b0\fn黑体\be0\bord0\shad0\fs26\fsp-2\c&H090909&\pos(884,448)\frz359.6}巨人全消失了
